    "YoungProjector[shape, content] returns the projector over the Young \
subgroup associated with content in the irreducible representation of the \
symmetric group associated with shape. YoungProjector[shape] represents an \
operator form of YoungProjector to be applied to a content. \
YoungProjector[shape, rep] represents an operator form and uses the array rep \
of matrices of adjacent transpositions in the symmetric group.", 
